{"title":"母亲的诗句","authors":["刘学努"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":7,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲的诗句"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘学努"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲一字不识"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我发表的诗句"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和每一封家信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是姐姐念给她听"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐姐出嫁了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲再接到我的信时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只好颠三倒四地翻阅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻阅儿子无尽的思念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲一字不识"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个远离家乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在边疆当兵站岗的儿子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是她"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"琅琅上口的诗句"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}